@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ozoatu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((0.99 - tmp) + wp.exp((v0 + 0.69 - v0 + 0.46)))
    tmp = (0.52 / tmp)
    v2 = (wp.cos(0.97) * (0.69 / (v1 + 0.55 * v1 + 0.16)))
    data[tid] = v0
